This is our secondÂ Meetup of 2013, to be held at our usual venue in Natick.

Swap themes:
1. Sun (or sun, moon, stars)
2. Steampunk

DEMO: Pat will lead us in a discussion/session about finishes for ATCs. Want that "finished" look for your own ATCs? Bring any finishes you have that you're not sure how to use and ask questions. We can all share knowledge about fixing images and other elements to make sure colors don't run, etc.
item.how_to_find_us: Use door near back of church, off parking lot
